INTRODUCTION

An alien force has evaded the planet. They are destroying civilization from one city to another... following, railtracks they headed towards a city... men in force, are trying hard to stop them... but to no avail ...
When all else failed, the city sent its best man to tackle the worst disaster it could ever have. The man, proudly known as 'The Guard'.
Who never fails, who never gives up, is standing like a firewall, between the life-throbbing city and the approaching threat. His only job is to stop the alien force from entering the city.
Now 'The Guard' is here... sorry Aliens! but no trespassing allowed.
INPUT CONTROL
For mobile, tablet & other touch screen devices: Use on-screen dailer to control the gunfire.
For Desktop: Use mouse to control the gunfire.
WATCH-OUT
Alien bullets. Each one drains 5% of your health.
Aliens: They are full with hazardous nuclear material. Don't come in contact with them. Each one takes 10% of your health.
POWER-UPS
Burgers: Take a quick bite, and get back 5% of your health.
Mugs: Filled with your favorite energy drink, they restore 10% of your health. Grab one quickly.
GAME OVER
Click 'Restart' to play again
or click 'Main Menu' to go back to main menu.
